data.name: acumatica_Content
data.value: With Power BI you can develop compelling visual reports that bring together your Acumatica ERP data (financials, distribution, manufacturing, accounting, CRM) and your other data sources in one place. Obtain a 360° view of your business in minutes with easy to use, drag and drop, pre-built dashboards and reports.

data.name: acumatica_Heading
data.value: Enhance your Acumatica data by integrating it with other applications in minutes.

data.name: acumatica_Name
data.value: Acumatica

data.name: acumatica_SubContent1
data.value: Identify broader correlations from your Acumatica data easily. With the flexibility of Power BI you can quickly gain insights into your data to uncover the hidden relationships or patterns leading to new opportunities to improve productivity and business operations.

data.name: acumatica_SubContent2
data.value: Compare your Acumatica CRM data side by side, against applications like Marketo marketing automation, and Google Analytics website data. Connect to dozens of other leading business applications in a few easy steps, leading to new insights and enhanced data clarity.

data.name: acumatica_SubContent3
data.value: Create and store visually impactful dashboards and reports safely. Share your reports with colleagues - anytime, anywhere. With the Microsoft industry-leading cloud computing platform, your data is always secure.
